{"tid":478200,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone X 工場請3000高校生日做11小時　不「實習」不許畢業","createTime":"2017-11-24T00:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T05:37:40.000Z","uid":25858,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ed3c6a154f982a1665b1f8e6fb960920cdc77838","tid":478200,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:01:39.000Z","msg":"iPhone X 在鄭州的富士康工場，被爆強制徵用學生每天最多上班 11 小時趕製手機。消息指高校生投訴需要在工場做 3 個月才能畢業，涉及人數達到 3,000 人。蘋果與富士康已對此事作出回應，指不會再讓高校生加班（每天工作 8 小時），但否認高校生是被強制到工場工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在英國《金融時報》報道裡面，有 6 位高校生受訪，表示曾在富士康在鄭州生產蘋果 iPhone X 的工場，常態地每天工作 11 小時。由於 6 人屬於「實習生」，在中國法律上加班工作是違法行為。有一位高校生指，他 1 日最多為 1200 部 iPhone X 組裝相機鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，高校生為了能夠畢業，需要在工場內進行 3 個月的「勞動體驗」，屬於強制性質。《金融時報》指出，在 9 月份鄭州城軌交通學校就派遣了 3,000 名年齡由 17 至 19 歲的學生到該工場工作。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果與富士康對報道作出回應，指高校生在工場加班的行為，已經被廠方指正。但否認高校生是被強制性送到工場工作。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果發言人指「蘋果注力於對本公司供應商所有員工以相應的尊嚴看待與表達敬意。」、「本公司已確認學生們的工作出於自發，並得到相應的工資與津貼，但廠方不應該允許他們加班工作」。<br />\n<br />\n有當地消息指現時實習生的工作時數已減至每天 8 小時，並不允許加班。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大貨到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39bc9a5b2ba9d4688ab88ac6e639d57a00e6f81","tid":478200,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:08:42.000Z","msg":"實習生整到d相機鏡頭入曬塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc672bb5eee0c49e5740767b0498a181c7cd683b","tid":478200,"uid":188,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:17:33.000Z","msg":"11個鍾就瓜瓜叫<br />\n香港人笑而不語"},{"pid":"bd29ea855a10cec1b5a063697391ddd03db4d892","tid":478200,"uid":70928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>11個鍾就瓜瓜叫<br />\n香港人笑而不語</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十一個鐘咁早放"},{"pid":"5023b02aa93e771565df532fc746daafbeb8249d","tid":478200,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:48:22.000Z","msg":"好想買多幾部iphone x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00c3d2b17085d8a750e7a1f2a6fa54bd3e97bb1","tid":478200,"uid":19908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:49:22.000Z","msg":"男嘅奴工 女嘅性奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5628f42a8349229f19c77ac85f95ef514e15d69","tid":478200,"uid":121306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"最好請多幾千個，等班炒家粥水都無得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5533849b22f73978ca7d80f838cb250985c5e679","tid":478200,"uid":10326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>實習生整到d相機鏡頭入曬塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重量不重質係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c6a20337191bfd8fabe0bced7d6d957c2eb776","tid":478200,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"qc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}